creator: Dedeman Hotels
descriptionHtml:
Dedeman Hotels application has been developed for you to get the best service from our hotel and have a perfect guest experience when you stay at Dedeman Hotels.

During your stay, you can benefit from Restaurant Reservation, SPA Reservation, Laundry, Housekeeping, Room Supplies, Maintenance for your room, Wake-Up Call, Concierge, Tray Collection, Porter Service, Late Check-out and Transfer request services by Dedeman Hotels mobile application.

Furthermore by the mobile application, you can benefit from tailor-made offers and discounts which are specialized for you, and get information about nearby attractions by city guides to make your stay memorable.

Even you can chat with our hotel staff regarding your guest service requests by the mobile application and send your requests and feedback to us directly. We will be working to provide the best service instantly by evaluating the surveys regarding your experiences which we will deliver by the application while you are using it.

Download and enhance your stay.
